query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.subdomain, p.assetsBaseUrl, a.id as asset_id, a.assetType, a.fileUrl 
FROM projects p 
LEFT JOIN assets a ON p.id = a.projectId 
WHERE p.name LIKE '%OpenClaw%' OR p.subdomain LIKE '%openclaw%'
ORDER BY a.assetType;
